## Overview

Skill Spell is an AI-driven learning platform that delivers personalized learning
roadmaps, adaptive assessments, and context-aware assistance for learners.

## What I Built

- Custom roadmap generator with curated resources (links, books, lectures)
- Context-aware chatbot using Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG)
- YouTube video summarization using Whisper.cpp
- OCR-based document understanding with vector search (ChromaDB)

## Tech Stack

- TensorFlow
- LangChain
- OpenAI
- Ollama
- ChromaDB
- Streamlit
- Docker

